---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import landing from '../data/landing.json';

const pageTitle = "Rules & Ranking | aira";
const pageDescription = "Official competition rules and ranking formula for aira Time Attack.";
---

<Layout
  title={pageTitle}
  description={pageDescription}
  canonicalUrl={landing.site.url + '/rules'}
  ogImage={landing.site.ogImage}
  siteName={landing.site.name}
  ogTitle={pageTitle}
  ogDescription={pageDescription}
  lang={landing.site.lang}
>
  <Header />
  <main class="bg-arena-bg min-h-screen">

    <!-- Page hero -->
    <div class="relative pt-24 pb-16 px-4 sm:px-6 border-b border-arena-border overflow-hidden">
      <div
        class="absolute inset-0 pointer-events-none"
        style="background-image: linear-gradient(to right, #e4e4e7 1px, transparent 1px), linear-gradient(to bottom, #e4e4e7 1px, transparent 1px); background-size: 48px 48px; opacity: 0.4;"
        aria-hidden="true"
      ></div>
      <div class="relative max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center">
        <span class="inline-block text-xs font-semibold tracking-widest text-orange-500 uppercase mb-4">Official Rules</span>
        <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-light tracking-tight text-arena-ink">
          Rules &amp; Ranking
        </h1>
        <p class="mt-6 text-lg text-arena-muted max-w-xl mx-auto">
          Everything you need to know to compete fairly and understand how rankings are calculated.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 py-16 space-y-12">

      <!-- Section: Time Attack Rules -->
      <section>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-6">
          <span class="inline-block w-1 h-6 bg-orange-500 rounded-full"></span>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-arena-ink">Time Attack — Competition Rules</h2>
        </div>

        <div class="rounded-2xl border border-arena-border bg-white p-8 shadow-sm space-y-8">

          <!-- Format -->
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-base font-semibold text-arena-ink mb-3">Format</h3>
            <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-arena-muted list-none">
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="mt-1 text-orange-400">▸</span> Solo race — 1 robot, 2 laps</li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="mt-1 text-orange-400">▸</span> Your objective: complete 2 laps in the shortest possible time while managing battery (SOC)</li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="mt-1 text-orange-400">▸</span> Any control mode is allowed: keyboard, CSV, rule-based, or neural network AI</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <!-- Registration -->
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-base font-semibold text-arena-ink mb-3">Registration &amp; Identity</h3>
            <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-arena-muted list-none">
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="mt-1 text-orange-400">▸</span> Your <code class="bg-zinc-100 text-zinc-700 px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded text-xs font-mono">NAME</code> in <code class="bg-zinc-100 text-zinc-700 px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded text-xs font-mono">config.txt</code> must match your aira account display name exactly</li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="mt-1 text-orange-400">▸</span> Allowed characters: A–Z, a–z, 0–9, underscore (<code class="bg-zinc-100 text-zinc-700 px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded text-xs font-mono">_</code>), up to 16 characters</li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="mt-1 text-orange-400">▸</span> Set <code class="bg-zinc-100 text-zinc-700 px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded text-xs font-mono">COMPETITION_NAME</code> to the active competition ID (e.g. <code class="bg-zinc-100 text-zinc-700 px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded text-xs font-mono">TimeAttack_2026_01</code>)</li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="mt-1 text-orange-400">▸</span> For competition mode, your <code class="bg-zinc-100 text-zinc-700 px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded text-xs font-mono">NAME</code> must be pre-registered. If not registered, an authentication error appears before the race starts</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <!-- Submission -->
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-base font-semibold text-arena-ink mb-3">Submitting a Result</h3>
            <ol class="space-y-2 text-sm text-arena-muted list-none">
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="shrink-0 w-5 h-5 mt-0.5 rounded-full bg-orange-100 text-orange-600 text-xs font-semibold flex items-center justify-center">1</span> Set <code class="bg-zinc-100 text-zinc-700 px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded text-xs font-mono">RACE_FLAG=1</code> in <code class="bg-zinc-100 text-zinc-700 px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded text-xs font-mono">config.txt</code> before running</li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="shrink-0 w-5 h-5 mt-0.5 rounded-full bg-orange-100 text-orange-600 text-xs font-semibold flex items-center justify-center">2</span> Complete the race — a <strong>Post Confirmation Panel</strong> appears when the race ends</li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="shrink-0 w-5 h-5 mt-0.5 rounded-full bg-orange-100 text-orange-600 text-xs font-semibold flex items-center justify-center">3</span> Review your result and click <strong>POST</strong> to submit to the leaderboard</li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="shrink-0 w-5 h-5 mt-0.5 rounded-full bg-orange-100 text-orange-600 text-xs font-semibold flex items-center justify-center">4</span> Only the fastest result across all robots in that run is submitted</li>
            </ol>
            <div class="mt-4 flex items-start gap-2 text-xs text-amber-700 bg-amber-50 border border-amber-200 rounded-lg px-4 py-3">
              <span class="mt-0.5 shrink-0">⚠</span>
              <span>Use <code class="font-mono">RACE_FLAG=0</code> during practice to avoid posting incomplete runs.</span>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Disqualification -->
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-base font-semibold text-arena-ink mb-3">Invalid Results</h3>
            <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-arena-muted list-none">
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="mt-1 text-zinc-400">✕</span> <strong>False Start</strong> — robot moves before the GO signal</li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="mt-1 text-zinc-400">✕</span> <strong>Battery Depleted</strong> — SOC reaches 0 before completing 2 laps</li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="mt-1 text-zinc-400">✕</span> <strong>Fallen</strong> — robot falls off the track</li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="mt-1 text-zinc-400">✕</span> <strong>Name mismatch</strong> — <code class="bg-zinc-100 text-zinc-700 px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded text-xs font-mono">NAME</code> not registered for the competition</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <!-- Platform note -->
          <div class="flex items-start gap-2 text-xs text-sky-700 bg-sky-50 border border-sky-200 rounded-lg px-4 py-3">
            <span class="mt-0.5 shrink-0">ℹ</span>
            <span>The simulator runs on <strong>Windows only</strong>. Mac/Linux support is planned for a future release.</span>
          </div>

        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- Section: Ranking Formula -->
      <section>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-6">
          <span class="inline-block w-1 h-6 bg-sky-500 rounded-full"></span>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-arena-ink">Ranking Formula</h2>
        </div>

        <div class="rounded-2xl border border-arena-border bg-white p-8 shadow-sm space-y-6">

          <p class="text-sm text-arena-muted">
            Rankings are calculated transparently so you always know exactly where you stand and why.
          </p>

          <!-- Primary score -->
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-base font-semibold text-arena-ink mb-3">Primary Score: Race Time</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-arena-muted mb-3">
              The ranking is determined by <strong>fastest 2-lap race time</strong>, measured from the GO signal to crossing the finish line on lap 2.
            </p>
            <div class="bg-zinc-950 text-zinc-100 rounded-xl px-5 py-4 font-mono text-xs">
              Score = race_time_ms at Finish (lower is better)
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Rules table -->
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-base font-semibold text-arena-ink mb-3">Ranking Rules</h3>
            <div class="overflow-x-auto">
              <table class="w-full text-sm text-left border-collapse">
                <thead>
                  <tr class="border-b border-arena-border">
                    <th class="pb-2 pr-4 font-semibold text-arena-ink">Rule</th>
                    <th class="pb-2 text-arena-ink font-semibold">Detail</th>
                  </tr>
                </thead>
                <tbody class="text-arena-muted">
                  <tr class="border-b border-arena-border">
                    <td class="py-3 pr-4 font-medium text-arena-ink whitespace-nowrap">Best result only</td>
                    <td class="py-3">Only your fastest submission appears on the leaderboard</td>
                  </tr>
                  <tr class="border-b border-arena-border">
                    <td class="py-3 pr-4 font-medium text-arena-ink whitespace-nowrap">Unlimited submissions</td>
                    <td class="py-3">You may submit as many times as you like during the competition period</td>
                  </tr>
                  <tr class="border-b border-arena-border">
                    <td class="py-3 pr-4 font-medium text-arena-ink whitespace-nowrap">Tiebreaker</td>
                    <td class="py-3">In the event of identical times, the earlier submission wins</td>
                  </tr>
                  <tr>
                    <td class="py-3 pr-4 font-medium text-arena-ink whitespace-nowrap">Battery</td>
                    <td class="py-3">Collisions drain SOC — aggressive driving risks battery depletion and disqualification</td>
                  </tr>
                </tbody>
              </table>
            </div>
          </div>

        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- Section: Head-to-Head (upcoming) -->
      <section>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-6">
          <span class="inline-block w-1 h-6 bg-zinc-300 rounded-full"></span>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-arena-ink">Head-to-Head Race <span class="ml-2 text-sm font-normal text-arena-muted">(Coming Soon)</span></h2>
        </div>

        <div class="rounded-2xl border border-arena-border bg-white p-8 shadow-sm opacity-60">
          <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-arena-muted list-none">
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="mt-1 text-zinc-400">▸</span> 5 robots race simultaneously on the same track</li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="mt-1 text-zinc-400">▸</span> Submit your <code class="bg-zinc-100 text-zinc-700 px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded text-xs font-mono">Robot1</code> folder as a ZIP to the designated submission URL</li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="mt-1 text-zinc-400">▸</span> Grid positions are assigned based on Time Attack ranking — faster qualifiers start at the front</li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="mt-1 text-zinc-400">▸</span> Races will be broadcast live or recorded on YouTube</li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="mt-1 text-zinc-400">▸</span> Full rules will be published when this format launches</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </section>

    </div>

    <!-- Bottom CTA -->
    <div class="border-t border-arena-border">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 py-16 text-center">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-light tracking-tight text-arena-ink">Ready to race?</h2>
        <p class="mt-3 text-arena-muted">Set up your environment and submit your first run.</p>
        <div class="mt-6 flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-center gap-3">
          <a
            href="/getting-started"
            class="inline-flex items-center px-8 py-3.5 text-base font-semibold text-white bg-orange-500 rounded-full hover:bg-orange-600 transition-colors"
          >
            Getting Started →
          </a>
          <a
            href="/competitions"
            class="inline-flex items-center px-8 py-3.5 text-base font-semibold text-arena-ink border border-arena-border rounded-full hover:border-zinc-400 transition-colors"
          >
            View Competitions
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

  </main>
  <Footer {...landing.footer} />
</Layout>
